01:02:30,290 --> 01:02:31,292
Sarah!

501
01:03:01,599 --> 01:03:04,240
Paul? Paul?

502
01:03:44,740 --> 01:03:46,128
Paul?

503
01:03:49,922 --> 01:03:52,883
This is 2-Carl-9.
