01:04:06,856 --> 01:04:07,856
Shit!

507
01:05:40,908 --> 01:05:42,868
Stop!

508
01:06:25,252 --> 01:06:28,277
Help, Sarah!

509
01:06:29,137 --> 01:06:31,668
